list.abstract: partner（英 [ˈpɑːtnə]，美 [ˈpɑːrtnər]），英语单词，作名词为合作者；股东；合伙人。作动词为做…的搭档；使合伙；成为搭档。短语搭配有business partner（商业伙伴）。例句为“Make sure you have a partner with you.（确保你有一个合作伙伴。）” partner相关近义词有comrade、associate等。

yingyinNormal.en: So he is now your partner, master.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以他现在是您的伙伴了，主人。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know what you're implying. Oh. Here is my very successful business partner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道你这话是什么意思。这位是我非常成功的生意合作伙伴。

yingyinNormal.en: I see a partner when it comes to Syria, or what's left of it. Let me try one of those.
yingyinNormal.zh: 叙利亚或者满目疮痍的叙利亚，可以成为合作伙伴。给我一个。

yingyinNormal.en: He and his research partner, Dr. Kim park, have come up with a model that predicts earthquakes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他和他的研究伙伴基姆帕克博士设计出了一个可以预测地震的理论模型。

yingyinNormal.en: Trench, through it, not over it. I'll remember. Hey, hey! Hey, wait up, partner! Hold on!
yingyinNormal.zh: 海沟，从下面过，别从上面过。我记住了，嘿，嘿! 嘿, 等等，伙伴！等等！

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and her friends are putting up their tents. Children, you must each find a partner to share your tent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇和朋友们搭起了帐篷。每一个人要找一个伙伴一起共用一个帐篷。

yingyinNormal.en: The scrutiny, the judgment. I'm partner less than a year.
yingyinNormal.zh: 监视，评判，我做合伙人还不到一年。

yingyinNormal.en: Worked beautifully, too. Until your partner started playing hero.
yingyinNormal.zh: 干得漂亮。直到你的搭档开始扮英雄。

yingyinNormal.en: Had you ever seen this partner? Howard Lyman? No. He's the oldest partner. He only comes in every now and then.
yingyinNormal.zh: 见过这位合伙人吗霍华德莱曼吗？没有，他是最年长的合伙人，偶尔才出现一次。

yingyinNormal.en: Why can't you be this fast when I'm your charades partner?
yingyinNormal.zh: 跟我猜字谜时，你反应怎么就没这么快？

yingyinNormal.en: Who's he? My partner, your other lawyer. Oh, the kid. Right.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他是谁？我的合伙人，你的另一位律师。那个小子啊。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm a partner, I'm adding va... Whose side are you on, anyway?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是合伙人，我能增加...不过你到底是站在哪一边啊？

yingyinNormal.en: We need people.The more the better. We need each other, partner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们需要人手越多越好，我们需要彼此，老兄。

yingyinNormal.en: That's real bad, partner. They suspend you for that kind of thing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这可坏了，拍档，这种是要被停职的。

yingyinNormal.en: Will wants me in the Chumhum meeting. Why? He wants a partner there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 威尔l想让我参加查查网公司的会议。为什么？他想要个合伙人参加。

yingyinNormal.en: This gun killed Officer Dempsey's partner at a routine traffic stop.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这把枪在一次常规交通违章处理中打死了邓普西警官的搭档。

yingyinNormal.en: You can rationalize it any way you want, but it would still. I'm not rationalizing anything. Whatever we do, it's a partner's decision. You're not a partner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想找什么借口都行，但这还是。我没找任何借口，不管要怎么做，那都由合伙人来定，而你不是合伙人。

yingyinNormal.en: Fusco? Your name sounds familiar. He's my partner. You can trust him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 弗斯科？这名字很耳熟。他是我搭档，可以信任。

yingyinNormal.en: I've heard about your partner's troubles. Uh, Curtis Agos. Cary Agos.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我听说了，你的合伙人有麻烦，科蒂斯艾格斯。凯里艾格斯。

yingyinNormal.en: Diane? David Lee and Damian are trying to remove you as managing partner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 戴安，大卫·李和达米恩想把你从管理合伙人的位置上踢下去。
